member.summary: If AutoFontSubstitution is disabled, GroupDocs.Conversion uses the DefaultFont for the substitution of missing fonts. If AutoFontSubstitution is enabled, GroupDocs.Conversion evaluates all the related fields in FontInfo (Panose, Sig etc) for the missing font and finds the closest match among the available font sources.
